A good father will never stop trying to straighten out his dumbass kids.  I am sure the Creator will not abandon us!<br><br>
It occurs to me that the greatest arguements usually occur when both parties are right (a fight to the death because of values)... or both parties are wrong (a fight to the death because of ignorance.)<br><br>
The war in Vietnam was both right and wrong.  Certainly it provides an arena for some after fighting.  The war encompassed a lot.. collectively, it is a huge problem.  A bale of hay is heavy... a straw is not!<br>
  <br>
Cookie is right and Cookie is wrong.. Tom is right and Tom is wrong!  So-oooo, big deal... welcome to the human race!<br><br>
Essentially, everyone is right and wrong, sometimes.. with the exceptions...God and helicopter pilots are never wrong and the rest are seldom correct... and most Marines don't know the difference (except when stood at attention.. or doing pushups.)<br><br>
I love all of you (except those who disagree with me and those who think the only good Indian is a dead Indian!)<br><br>
Mustang Two Four.. making hay while the sun shines!
